# Slider Design

**Tier:** 1-Beginner

Example Carousel Image.

## User Stories

-   [ ] User can click on "arrow next" and "Arrow back" for next image and previous image 
-   [ ] User can see imae display multiple image for every "X" seconds 

## Bonus features

-   [ ] Add animation to the slides
-   [ ] Add text over the slides

## Useful links and resources

-   [Unsplash](https://unsplash.com/) for free images

